  "title": "Enable a grace period for Identity Governance Access Certification",
  "description": "During an access certification, some organizations might allow for revoke decisions. Some campaigns implement a grace period where end users retain access to the resource for a period before their access is revoked. This template enables this configuration for a campaign, applying the revoke decision at a future date. The date is determined according to the number of days granted as a grace period.",
